        <item>
            <title>【评测】Fujifilm INSTAX Pal 迷你相机，的骰便携 + 一按即印又得、连落电话再印又得</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/fujifilm-instax-pal-3/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fujifilm-instax-pal-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/fujifilm-instax-pal-3/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 12:38:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相机测试]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[fujifilm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm Instax]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm INSTAX Pal]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[即影即有相机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202492</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>现今社会相信大家人手都会有部智能电话，随时也可以和朋友「Selfie」留念。数码相片虽然清晰且容易分享，可是总会让人感觉缺了点「温度」。Fujifilm 的 instax 系列即影即有相机一直广受欢迎，即使智能手机摄影普及后仍然非常有人气。最近 Fujifilm instax 系列又添一员，推出只有乒乓波大小的全新 INSTAX Pal 小型相机，让摄影变得更轻松有趣。今日小编就和 unwire 记者 Weak 妹、Anna 测试 Fujifilm 这部 INSTAX Pal 小型相机，以下会和大家分享一下用后感。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202895" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09204-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09204-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09204-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09204.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>5 种颜色选择，容易衬衫</h2><p>Fujifilm INSTAX 系列在颜色选择方面一向不会吝啬，这次 Fujifilm 一口气推出了乳白、淡粉红、牛油果绿、薰衣草蓝及宝石黑 5 种颜色，而小编收到的就是牛油果绿。清新得来又有点时尚感觉，容易衬衫。质感方面，机身使用防滑的雾面塑胶质料，让用家拍照时不容易跣手。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200346 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN00281-694x462.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN00281-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN00281-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN00281.jpg 1280w" alt="" width="694" height="462" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲乳白、淡粉红、牛油果绿、薰衣草蓝及宝石黑</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202894" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09202-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09202-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09202-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09202.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编收到的牛油果绿色 INSTAX Pal</p><h2>外型的骰，轻便易携</h2><div><p>INSTAX Pal 机身整体尺寸是 42.3 x 44.4 x 43mm (不包括突出部件)，而且仅重 41 g，当作吊饰挂在身上、袋上亦不会觉得重，方便用家随时带住 INSTAX Pal 出街，随时影靓相。</p></div><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09731-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09731-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09731-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09731.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>单手操控非常方便，一按即拍照</h2><p>INSTAX Pal 虽然机仔细细采用掌上的骰设计，但其亦五脏俱全，有多种功能，如果只需拍照，简单按下后面的快门按钮即可，此模式下可利用广角镜头进行智能手机难以实现的高位或锐角拍摄，只要用单手即可轻松地高炒或以锐角进行拍摄。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09755-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09755-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09755-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09755.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲快门设于机背，单手一按就可拍照</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203452" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09832-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09832-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09832-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09832.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲超广角镜头非常方便自拍，即使有多几个朋友也能应付自如</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203453" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09835-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09835-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09835-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09835.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身细细配备广角镜，低炒也非常轻松</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09828-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09828-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09828-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09828.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>续航力高，充满电可以影 240 张</h2><p>相机透过 USB Type-C 接口充电，内置锂离子电池充满电后可连续拍摄约 240 张。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09199-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09199-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09199-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09199.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身只有拍照按钮、USB-C 接口及开关掣</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09200-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09200-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09200-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09200.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲底部设有标准尺寸脚架孔及模式转换键</p><h2>多功能圈套配件，可取景、套在手、当脚架</h2><p>相机配有多功能环配件，可套于手上以防止意外掉落，甚至在拍摄合照时可用作简化的取景器和相机支架。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202892" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09748-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09748-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09748-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09748.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可充当简单取景器</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09194-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09194-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09194-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09194.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲也可当作轻便脚架</p><h2>拍摄模式 1：「即影即有」  一按即拍马上印</h2><p>作为即影即有，当然要有「即刻影即刻有」的功能。要启用「即影即有」功能，首先你身边要有一部有菲林而且已启动电源的即影即有打印机，之后你要检查一下 INSTAX Pal 底部是否已设定为「L」模式（Link 模式）。设定为「L」模式后，即可与 INSTAX Link 系列直接进行蓝牙连接，而无需使用专用应用程式。在此模式下，使用 INSTAX Pal 拍摄的照片会立即从 INSTAX Link 打印机自动列印出来，就像使用即影即有相机一样。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203466" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09860-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09860-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09860-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09860.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203467" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09861-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09861-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09861-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09861.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲要留意是否已设定为「L 模式」</p><p>设定为 L 模式后，按下相机快门键，INSTAX Pal 就会自动开始倒计时，计时期间会发出滴滴声，约 5 秒钟后，相机就会发出「滴答」水滴声，示意已经拍摄随后 INSTAX Pal 会自动连接最近的 INSTAX 打印机列印相片。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203469" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09881-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09881-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09881-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09881.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲INSTAX Pal 会自动连接最近的 INSTAX 打印机</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09898-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09898-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09898-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09898.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这样就可以「即影即有」</p><h2>拍摄模式 2：连接手机 LiveView、遥控拍照后再慢慢印</h2><p>INSTAX Pal 的另一个玩法，是连接到智能电话，利用 INSTAX Pal 拍照后，在电话上执相、加效果再印。用家可下载 Fujifilm 的「INSTAX Pal」应用程式后，以蓝牙连接 INSTAX Pal 后就能以电话遥控拍照。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203455" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09836-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09836-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09836-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09836.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下载应用程式后就能用电话远距离控制 INSTAX Pal</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203457" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203458" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「远端模式」可以从手机看到 INSTAX Pal 拍摄画面</p><p>智能电话拍照后，透过蓝牙连接 INSTAX Link 系列打印机，即可打印拍到的 instax 菲林相片。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203459" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-1-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-1-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-1-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-1.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在电话上构好图，按快门键</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203460" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834575_y-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834575_y-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834575_y-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834575_y.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Fujifilm 的应用程式会让你预览列印出来的样子<img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203461" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834581_y-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834581_y-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834581_y-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834581_y.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲确认要列印后就可以传送至 mini LINK 应用程式，连接 INSTAX Link 系列打印机</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203462" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09902-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09902-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09902-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09902.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203463" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09906-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09906-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09906-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09906.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲接下来就只需要等待相片显影（大约 90 秒至 2 分钟）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09907-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09907-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09907-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09907.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲你就可以有一张即影即有</p><p><span lang="EN-US">Fujifilm INSTAX Pal 经已正式</span>发售，备有乳白、淡粉红、牛油果绿、薰衣草蓝及宝石黑，建议零售价为 <span lang="EN-US">$780（宝石黑售价为 $950）。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203474" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09831-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09831-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09831-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09831.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203475" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09886-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09886-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09886-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09886.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/fujifilm-instax-pal-3/dc/">【评测】Fujifilm INSTAX Pal 迷你相机，的骰便携 + 一按即印又得、连落电话再印又得</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
